TY  - JOUR
TI  - Competitive Equilibria in Markets with a Continuum of Traders and Incomplete Preferences
AU  - Schmeidler, David
AB  - [Existence of competitive equilibrium in a market model introduced by Robert J. Aumann is proved. This paper generalized Aumann's result and simplifies his proof.]
